## Schema deviation from proposal text

The proposal stated the parsed mapping has top-level `hits` and `rules` keys. The actual live shape (verified against group-pas-dev) nests under `decisionTable.{hitPolicy, inputs, outputs, rules}` with per-rule `when`/`then` dicts. Design + widget follow the live shape; proposal text is now stale, will be corrected in the Implementation notes commit.

